<main class="first">
    <main class="hero-body d-flex">
        <div class="hero-text-area d-flex flex-column justify-content-center ">
            <h2 class="text-white">
                A privacy-focused platform to monitor and archive business
                communications
            </h2>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <p>
                    Real-time recognition and alerting of compliance and data loss
                    based on images, videos, and text from social media and other
                    digital channels
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-1">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <p>
                    GDPR compliant monitoring and data archiving functionality,
                    enables our clients to be in line with requirements from their
                    respective regulatory bodies
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <button
                        class="btn-accent mt-4"
                        data-target="#requestDemo"
                        data-toggle="modal"
                >
                    Request Demo
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
                class="helmet w-50 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
        >
            <img
                    alt=""
                    class="img-fluid"
                    src="images/icons/DeepView_Img1.png"
            />
        </div>
    </main>
    <div class="dive-deeper">
        <p class="p-0 m-0">DIVE DEEPER</p>
        <hr class="line"/>
    </div>
</main>
<main class="section-two central">
    <div class="the-problem d-flex">
        <div
                class="problem-image d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
        >
            <img
                    alt=""
                    src="images/icons/DeepView_DiverProblem_SVG.svg"
                    width="100%"
            />
        </div>
        <div
                class=" problem-text d-flex flex-column justify-content-center p-3"
        >
            <h3 class="text-white">The Problem</h3>
            <div class="text-white">
                Social media apps and channels are not built to be compliant or
                secure.
            </div>
            <div class="text-point p-0 mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div class="">
                    Current digital risk monitoring solutions cannot read photos and
                    videos
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div>
                    Archiving and monitoring solutions do not meet privacy and GDPR
                    standards, especially on BYOD
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div>
                    Reputations and security are risked daily with enthusiastic
                    employees posting Instagram photos and videos on LinkedIn
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class=" d-flex the-solution">
        <div class="problem-text d-flex flex-column justify-content-center p-3">
            <h3 class="text-white">Our Solution</h3>
            <div class="text-white">
                The first platform to automate the entire end-to-end monitoring
                lifecycle with an enterprise-wide regulatory intelligence, including
                GDPR.
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div>
                    Real-time alerts for fast response to data leaks via video, text
                    and photo and organizations awareness of public data leaks
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div>
                    Evidence to regulators of ‘best-practice’ in data monitoring and
                    archiving
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-point mt-3">
                <img alt="" src="images/icons/check-mark.svg"/>
                <div>
                    Under 120 seconds onboarding time, tailored to specific
                    organizations and key risk personal
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
                class="problem-image d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
        >
            <img
                    alt=""
                    src="images/icons/DeepView_DiverSolution_SVG.svg"
                    width="100%"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div
            class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column mt-5 products mx-auto"
    >
        <h3 class="text-white">
            Our Products
        </h3>
        <div class="text-center mt-3 text-white opacity">
            DeepView delivers a unified platform for managing risk on digital
            platforms. One interactive secure portal allowing our ‘Buddies’ to
            enable employees to engage their networks securely and compliantly.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-5 guards">
        <div class="d-flex box flex-column box-container ">
            <div class=" box-area">
                <img
                        alt=""
