            <p class="text-white pt-3 opacity">
            <span class="accent opacity">
              Archiving And Record Keeping
            </span>
                For Cooperate Social Media.
            </p>
            <p
                    class="accent read opacity"
                    data-target="#corpguard"
                    data-toggle="modal"
