                Read more
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex box flex-column box-container">
            <div class="box-area">
                <img
                        alt=""
                        height="100px"
                        src="images/icons/DV_textEffect_TrainingGuard.png"
                />
            </div>

            <p class="text-white pt-3 opacity">
                Promoting Good Practices And
                <span class="opacity accent">Social Media Policy</span>.
            </p>

            <p
                    class="accent read opacity"
                    data-target="#trainingguard"
                    data-toggle="modal"
            >
                Read more
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="report d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
        <div class=" text-center mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-white opacity reporting">
                Reporting, Archiving and Better Digital <br/>
                Safety
            </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="image-cont">
            <img
                    alt=""
                    class="img-fluid"
                    src="images/icons/DeepView ScreenShot.png"
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
            class=" d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center mt-5 "
    >
        <h3 class="text-white opacity mt-5">Did You Know</h3>
        <div class="owl-carousel owl-theme carousel mt-5">
            <div class="sixty-five">
                <div class="image-back">
                    <img
                            alt=""
                            class="image-dive"
                            src="images/icons/DeepView_DiverHead_SVG.svg"
                    />
                </div>
                <h1 class="accent">60%</h1>
                <h5 class="text-white pt-2">
                    of information to hack a company can be found on Instagram
                </h5>
                <p class="text-white opacity pt-3">
                    According to Rachel Tobac, renowned social engineer, 60% of the
                    information needed to hack a company is found on Instagram as
                    employees inadvertently share confidential data.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sixty-five">
                <div class="image-back">
                    <img
                            alt=""
                            class="image-dive"
                            src="images/icons/DeepView_DiverHead_SVG.svg"
                    />
                </div>
                <h1 class="accent">65%</h1>
                <h5 class="text-white pt-2">
                    businesses worried that consumer chat apps can create a security
                    "loophole"
                </h5>
                <p class="text-white opacity pt-3">
                    Half were troubled by their inability to monitor and audit
                    employee communications. Ovum’s 2017 “Secure Enterprise Messaging”
                    survey of 300 businesses.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="sixty-five">
                <div class="image-back">
                    <img
                            alt=""
                            class="image-dive"
                            src="images/icons/DeepView_DiverHead_SVG.svg"
                    />
                </div>
                <h1 class="accent">50%</h1>
                <h5 class="text-white pt-2">
                    more likely to achieve sales quota when teams are engaged on
                    social media
                </h5>
                <p class="text-white opacity pt-3">
                    Research from LinkedIn and Hootsuite found that executives have a
                    key role to play in using social media to enhance the reputation
                    of their firms, attract talent, and increase sales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="welcome-to-deep the-problem d-flex">
        <div
                class=" problem-image d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center opacity"
        >
            <img
                    alt=""
                    src="images/icons//DeepView_DiverFooter_SVG.svg"
                    width="100%"
            />
        </div>
        <div
                class="problem-text d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
        >
            <div
                    class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-start p-3"
            >
                <h3 class="text-white opacity footer-text">
                    Welcome to DeepView<br/>
                    Come dive with us
                </h3>

                <button
                        class="btn-accent mt-4"
                        data-target="#requestDemo"
                        data-toggle="modal"
                >
                    Request Demo
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
